ounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8\"><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-background shadow-xl text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-4 max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 text-foreground bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm\">Feature Detail</div></div><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Manajemen Data Warga</h1><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground/90 leading-relaxed\">Kelola data penghuni secara digital, aman, dan mudah dicari kapan saja.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container py-16 md:py-24\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2 space-y-12\"><div class=\"space-y-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Tentang Fitur Ini</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Database warga yang terpusat dan aman. Memudahkan pendataan penghuni tetap, penyewa, hingga kendaraan yang dimiliki.</p><div class=\"space-y-6 pt-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Keuntungan Utama</h3><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border bg-card hover:bg-accent/50 transition-color